Curl and WGET
interact with HTTP,HTTPS,FTP protocols
curl- displays ASCII
  curl http://172.16.82.106 (to specify port add :<port#> to end)
  curl ftp://
wget - downloads (-r recursive)
  wget -r http:// * * * *
  wget -r ftp:// * * * * 


